ROD Stewart Releases New Song Stop Loving Her Today Rod Stewart has released a new song. Stop Loving Her Today is the only new material to appear on his forthcoming album. ‘You’re In My Heart: Rod Stewart With The Royal Philharmonic Orchestra’. The track is a guitar-led ballad that’s given a theatrical spin by the accompanying orchestra and choir. It arrives ahead of the veteran performer’s winter UK and Ireland arena tour, whick kicks off in Manchester on November 23 and concludes with a three-night stand at London’s O2 Arena in December.